:: Inventory [widget]

<<widget "inventory">>

<<if $wood is 1>>
You're carrying a plank of wood.
<br>
<</if>>

<<if $iron is 1>>
You're carrying an iron slag chunk.
<br>
<</if>>

<<if $wood gt 1>>
You're carrying <<print $wood>> wood planks.
<br>
<</if>>

<<if $iron gt 1>>
You're carrying <<print $iron>> iron slag chunks.
<br>
<</if>>

<<if $iron and $wood is 0>>
You're carrying nothing.
<br>
<</if>>

<</widget>>